        <h1>Browser State</h1>
        <ul class="mainlist flex">
            <li class="incremental no-bullet">
                <b>Challenge</b>
                <ul class="circle-bullet">
                    <li>Emulated devices must not share browser data</li>
                    <li>Actual devices don't share browser data -> Emulated devices should also not share browser data</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li class="incremental no-bullet">
                <b>Solution</b>
                <ul class="circle-bullet">
                    <li>Local DNS Server (rainbow-dns)</li>
                    <li>Each emulated device gets its own subdomain based on its ID</li>
                    <li>Unknown domains are forwarded to the usual DNS server</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
