        <h1>Event Capturing</h1>
        <ul class="mainlist flex">
            <li class="incremental no-bullet">
                <b>Challenge</b>
                <ul class="circle-bullet">
                    <li>
                        We must receive all events before anyone else receives them
                        <ul>
                            <li>Page could be modified</li>
                            <li>Events could be stopped from propagating</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li class="incremental no-bullet">
                <b>Solution</b>
                <ul class="circle-bullet">
                    <li>Include a script at the top of the page that is tested</li>
                    <li>Script adds event handlers before any other event handlers can be added</li>
                    <li>Add event handlers on the document itself with event capturing</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </op-view>

