        <h1>Accurate Event Visualization</h1>
        <ul class="mainlist flex">
            <li class="incremental no-bullet">
                <b>Challenge</b>
                <ul class="circle-bullet">
                    <li>Event visualization must represent the true timing of events if timing is to be configured using drag and drop</li>
                    <li>Each element that represents an event requires some space</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li class="incremental no-bullet">
                <b>Solution</b>
                <ul class="circle-bullet">
                    <li>Events are grouped based on their timing</li>
                    <li>Take the first event that needs to be visualized, then take all events that occur within x milliseconds of the first event</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
